        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【#休息日如何补觉更有效#[困][睡]】长期熬夜会改变人体生物钟，如果补觉不当反而更影响睡眠。熬夜党假期如何补觉？北京大学第六医院睡眠医学中心孙伟：①适当早...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E6%97%A5%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%A1%A5%E8%A7%89%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E6%97%A5%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%A1%A5%E8%A7%89%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#休息日如何补觉更有效#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[困]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kun-0f87c3e1f8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[睡]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuijiao-4cb62c7d81.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】长期熬夜会改变人体生物钟，如果补觉不当反而更影响睡眠。熬夜党假期如何补觉？北京大学第六医院睡眠医学中心孙伟：①适当早睡或晚起，以半小时到1小时为宜；②下午2点前午睡，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8D%88%E7%9D%A1%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A5%E5%86%85%E5%B0%B1%E5%A5%BD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8D%88%E7%9D%A1%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A5%E5%86%85%E5%B0%B1%E5%A5%BD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#午睡时间半小时以内就好#</span></a>；③夜间给睡眠多留一点时间，尽量避免熬夜。戳👇🏻一起get好睡眠！ <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4861702861422612" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hafjzjm1pzj614s1ide8102.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/IKFetF4dlx082CtmMxYI01041200nw5S0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1172.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674870083&amp;ssig=jt6sScVBdn&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ayTudTOWlx082CtotZos01041200dB2n0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x880.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674870083&amp;ssig=qtNkmsJAiw&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/FWJAtcKzlx082CtndXD2010412007eJv0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x584.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674870083&amp;ssig=0a5O1pFTPo&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4861702861422612&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
